text: Heliophanus kilimanjaroensis is a jumping spider species in the genus Heliophanus. It was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 1986 and is found in Tanzania. ==References== Category:Spiders described in 1986 Category:Fauna of Tanzania Category:Salticidae Category:Spiders of Africa Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
title: Heliophanus kilimanjaroensis
